        This create a new experiment
        Parameters:
        description - This is the description of experiments
        isEnded - This is to show whether the experiment has ended
        isPublished - This is to show whether the experiment has published
        minTrials - This is how many trials needed
        locationRequired - This is to show whether the experiment need location
        experimentType - This is to show which type the experiment is
        name - This is the name of experiments
        userName - This is the owner of experiments
